        "",
        "* `escrow_id`       — 32-byte UUID; used as PDA seed and stored for signing.",
        "* `amount`          — USDC micro-units (6 decimals; 1 USDC = 1_000_000).",
        "* `duration_secs`   — 0 for Flash, > 0 for Beam.",
        "* `escrow_type_val` — 0 = Flash, 1 = Beam."
